Package: AvianViromeDB
Title: Avian Virome Database
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jinlong", "Ru", , "jinlong.ru@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive database and interactive web application for exploring
    avian bacteriophage (virome) sequences. This database contains public NGS 
    sequencing data that has been assembled, annotated, and categorized to provide
    a valuable resource for researchers studying avian viromes.
